data.description: Motivated Seller. Seller is offering 2/1 buy down and 3 year home warranty. Rare 2+ acre Spanish Hacienda boasts unique architecture with rustic accents, wood framed windows, concrete construction and jaw dropping 360-degree views. The beamed entrance frames an authentic 165+ year-old Mission door perfectly. Hand painted Mexican tile, 2 wood burning fireplaces & a huge soaking tub, bring out the southwest character of the home. The courtyards/patios are perfect for those who love to host gatherings in an impressive location. Minutes from the I-17, Carefree Hwy, TSMC, this estate offers a gated drive, over 2 acres of usable/buildable land, PRIVATE WELL, owned solar, oversize 2 car garage with wall to wall cabinets/work bench, & top of the line water filtration system. No HOA and plenty of room. Bring your toys! Horses too.
